messages.author: Central Command
messages.body:
Security Report

Thanks to the tireless efforts of our security and intelligence divisions, there are currently no credible threats to Maconha Station 13. All station construction projects have been authorized. Have a secure shift!

messages.author: Central Command
messages.body:
Collision Alert

Stray cargo pod detected on long-range scanners. Expected location of impact: Fore Maintenance.

messages.author: Central Command
messages.body:
Migration Alert

Bioscans indicate that not more than 15 mice have swarmed into maintenance areas.

messages.author: Central Command
messages.body:
Anomaly Alert

High levels of radiation detected near the station. Maintenance is best shielded from radiation.

messages.author: Central Command
messages.body:
Anomaly Alert

The radiation threat has passed. Please return to your workplaces.

messages.author: Central Command Update
messages.body: Atençao crew inspeçao de rotina sera conduzida na station, estamos enviando um almirante para a station

messages.author: Central Command
messages.body:
CentCom Diplomatic Corps

Cargo: The Spider Clan has sent us a mysterious gift. Can we ship it to you to see what's inside?

messages.author: Central Command
messages.body:
Cargo shuttle commandeered by CentCom.

The cargo shuttle should return in five minutes. Have some supply points for your trouble.

messages.author: Central Command Update
messages.body: scan de sensores reporta um ponto na orbita da station

messages.author: Central Command Update
messages.body: um ponto no radar... ja sumiu

messages.author: Central Command
messages.body:
Critical Power Failure

Abnormal activity detected in Maconha Station 13's powernet. As a precautionary measure, the station's power will be shut off for an indeterminate duration.

messages.author: Central Command
messages.body:
Anomaly Alert

Localized hyper-energetic flux wave detected on long range scanners. Expected location: Teleporter Room.

messages.author: Central Command
messages.body:
Meteor Alert

Meteors have been detected on a collision course with the station towards the fore. Estimated time until impact: 344 seconds.

messages.author: Central Command
messages.body:
Anomaly Alert

Localized hyper-energetic flux wave detected on long range scanners. Expected location: Warehouse.

messages.author: Central Command
messages.body:
Anomaly Alert

Localized hyper-energetic flux wave detected on long range scanners. Expected location: Construction Area.

messages.author: Central Command
messages.body:
Anomaly Alert

High levels of radiation detected near the station. Maintenance is best shielded from radiation.

messages.author: Central Command
messages.body:
Anomaly Alert

The radiation threat has passed. Please return to your workplaces.
